This paper discusses the implementation of deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs) on field-programmable gate arrays (FPGAs), which falls under the categories of computer architecture (cs.AR), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), embedded systems (cs.ET), systems and control (cs.SY), and programming languages (cs.PL).
